Package: transformR
Title: Find Optimal Data Transformations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Zhijun Feng", email = "fengzhj18@sina.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for finding the optimal transformation for skewed data
    through multiple methods including square root, Box-Cox, Yeo-Johnson, inverse,
    rank normalization, and hyperbolic arcsine transformations. The package evaluates
    each transformation based on normality measures and recommends the best approach.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
